com.google.cloud

Interface FieldSelector

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BigQuery.DatasetField, BigQuery.JobField, BigQuery.TableField, Compute.AddressField, Compute.DiskField, Compute.DiskTypeField, Compute.ImageField, Compute.InstanceField, Compute.LicenseField, Compute.MachineTypeField, Compute.NetworkField, Compute.OperationField, Compute.RegionField, Compute.SnapshotField, Compute.SubnetworkField, Compute.ZoneField, Dns.ChangeRequestField, Dns.ProjectField, Dns.RecordSetField, Dns.ZoneField, InstanceInfo.InstanceField, ResourceManager.ProjectField, Storage.BlobField, Storage.BucketField

    public interface FieldSelector
    Interface for Google Cloud resource's fields. Implementations of this interface can be used to select only desired fields from a returned Google Cloud resource.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static class  FieldSelector.Helper
      A helper class used to build composite selectors given a number of fields.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      String getSelector()
      Returns a string selector.

    • Method Detail

      • getSelector

        String getSelector()
        Returns a string selector. This selector is passed to a Google Cloud service (possibly with other field selectors) to specify which resource fields should be returned by an API call.
